'''Groshik's [[Cantina/Legends|Cantina]]''' was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Apatros/Legends|Apatros]]. It was owned by the [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] [[Groshik]], who also served as the bartender. It was a popular hangout for [[Cortosis/Legends|cortosis]] miners. The bar was made to look like it was three stories high, when in reality the top two levels were colored glass made to give an illusion of importance. It contained [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]] tables. A portion of the cantina's profits were given to [[Outer Rim Oreworks Company|ORO]] as required by the company which dominated Apatros. The young miner [[Darth Bane/Legends|Dessel]], who would later become Darth Bane, played sabacc here, and once won a small fortune from a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Ensign/Legends|ensign]], nearly starting a riot.

